{"tid":499643,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【SBS歌謠大戰】Red Velvet與TWICE扮FIN.K.L　Wanna One做H.O.T","createTime":"2017-12-15T05:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T06:08:16.000Z","uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"97ec8ee26c7ddf8baa521298d2d379bdf04f834f","tid":499643,"uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/130110_8b9b52c29406431fa56802fc5b5b5d46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F130110_8b9b52c29406431fa56802fc5b5b5d46.jpg&h=19bbebf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【SBS歌謠大戰】Red Velvet與TWICE扮FIN.K.L　Wanna One做H.O.T</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/130146_f8217d632c53c50a682706c633462fa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F130146_f8217d632c53c50a682706c633462fa5.jpg&h=e820a096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">未知由Red Velvet和TWICE成員合作扮的韓國第一代女團FIN.K.L會有什麼不同呢？（網上圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/130300_20df16c3a39b99732f5fa760ae07fa7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F130300_20df16c3a39b99732f5fa760ae07fa7e.jpg&h=016c689c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTWICE成員多賢的調皮絕對可以為FIN.K.L的歌帶來新活力！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/130339_8cc0bb77e14b7c1fd23e4914d0c370ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F130339_8cc0bb77e14b7c1fd23e4914d0c370ee.jpg&h=723beea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/130339_dfd2146d73d13a88d6984771a039cc37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F130339_dfd2146d73d13a88d6984771a039cc37.jpg&h=1b2e65fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/130340_68a1a58d730b581c9fda739cdd3eef9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F130340_68a1a58d730b581c9fda739cdd3eef9b.jpg&h=a9ac458b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/130340_93b511c14ea1e6a55a368d3ca4c2c7c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F130340_93b511c14ea1e6a55a368d3ca4c2c7c9.jpg&h=fa07bb66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/130341_82942fd8e436c77c3890a14e9c01ad6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F130341_82942fd8e436c77c3890a14e9c01ad6e.jpg&h=037f841c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/130342_010d60c6ab70ec2488d32ca744ad8514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F130342_010d60c6ab70ec2488d32ca744ad8514.jpg&h=8337bfec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《SBS歌謠大戰》將於12月25日舉行，大家都好期待今年有咩表演。今日韓媒就報道兩大人氣女團TWICE同Red Velvet將會有特別合作舞台，扮演由李孝利、玉珠鉉、李真、成宥利組成的韓國第一代女團FIN.K.L，而Wanna One都會有成員扮韓國第一代男團H.O.T，令大家都好期待。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/130414_dc305e427ac123df14b5955f3eaea582.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F130414_dc305e427ac123df14b5955f3eaea582.jpg&h=1023571b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信大家都想睇下Wanna One扮H.O.T啦！（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/15/130439_57ab4e2a70bedba281f765f6e9dc310a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F130439_57ab4e2a70bedba281f765f6e9dc310a.jpg&h=cc1d8450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWanna One成員姜丹尼爾、黃旼炫、河成雲、邕聖祐、朴佑鎭係《SBS歌謠大戰》都有特別舞台架！（網上圖片）"},{"pid":"5d643201ee7b776a0a8a8065646de55ce3d8a14c","tid":499643,"uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:05:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9F%93%E8%BF%B7/141569/-SBS%E6%AD%8C%E8%AC%A0%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B0-Red-Velvet%E8%88%87TWICE%E6%89%AEFIN-K-L-Wanna-One%E5%81%9AH-O-T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E8%25BF%25B7%2F141569%2F-SBS%25E6%25AD%258C%25E8%25AC%25A0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2588%25B0-Red-Velvet%25E8%2588%2587TWICE%25E6%2589%25AEFIN-K-L-Wanna-One%25E5%2581%259AH-O-T&d=TNOiLsxCBh2L6hAYJQdfLpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=9db2498a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9F%93%E8%BF%B7/141569/-SBS%E6%AD%8C%E8%AC%A0%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B0-Red-Velvet%E8%88%87TWICE%E6%89%AEFIN-K-L-Wanna-One%E5%81%9AH-O-T</a>"},{"pid":"c654bc683fa823bbbe8483112cefca718696f5e2","tid":499643,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:07:27.000Z","msg":"Nayeon個嘴想點😂"},{"pid":"2175c085de275ba6388cc1bee422ca05ea9f4866","tid":499643,"uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Nayeon個嘴想點😂</blockquote><br />\n好得意"},{"pid":"ba8ded0e2eda493a78b6d64bd36a78e51a767f1f","tid":499643,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:08:16.000Z","msg":"多賢正撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}